## 1) System goals and constraints

This implementation targets a practical chat system baseline with:

- `1-1 + group` chat
- realtime WebSocket communication
- reliability-oriented write path (transactional persistence first, asynchronous publish later)
- local single-node deployment with separate processes (`gateway`, `api`, `worker`, `postgres`, `redis`)

