## 8) End-to-end flow examples

## Send message

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant Core
    participant Pg as PostgreSQL
    participant Worker
    participant Redis

    Client->>Gateway: send_message
    Gateway->>Core: CreateMessage
    Core->>Pg: tx(insert messages + outbox_events)
    Core-->>Gateway: message + seq
    Gateway-->>Client: server_ack
    Worker->>Pg: select pending outbox
    Worker->>Redis: XADD stream
    Worker->>Pg: mark published
```

## ACK pipeline (phase 3)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant Core
    participant Pg as PostgreSQL

    Client->>Gateway: ack_delivery
    Gateway->>Core: RecordDeliveryAck
    Core->>Pg: insert receipt(delivered) idempotent
    Core->>Pg: insert outbox message.delivery_ack
    Gateway-->>Client: delivery_ack_ok

    Client->>Gateway: ack_read
    Gateway->>Core: RecordReadAck
    Core->>Pg: validate target message seq
    Core->>Pg: advance read pointer if seq greater
    Core->>Pg: insert receipt(read) idempotent
    Core->>Pg: insert outbox message.read_ack
    Gateway-->>Client: read_ack_ok
```

